---
title: Pesto Chicken Burger and Herby Potatoes with truffle mayo sauce
description: This Italian-inspired burger features a moreish pesto drizzle, truffle mayo and perhaps best of all, a golden chicken breast sandwiched between two beautiful brioche buns. As if that's not enough, herby baby potatoes round out the dish.
